{"tid":590953,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮：禁止Broadcom收購Qualcomm　因會威脅國家安全","createTime":"2018-03-13T06:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T10:04:30.000Z","uid":47132,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc375f824554ed4ae1603a00cf5400d8c32e567","tid":590953,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:03:17.000Z","msg":"總統特朗普（Donald Trump）周一表示，有可靠證據顯示博通及其子公司或會透過今次的併購案採取行動，威脅並損害美國的國家安全，故必須即時及永久禁止兩間公司進行併購。<br />\n<br />\n高通2017年11月拒絕博通的收購提案，後者上月初宣布提高收購高通的出價，由每股作價70美元提高至82美元，有關提案已惹來美國外商投資委員會（CFIUS）展開調查；CFIUS由美國財政部主導，以調查該宗交易是否讓外國投資者控制美國企業，從而危及美國國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n博通周一發表聲明回應，稱公司強烈反對收購高通會構成威脅國家安全的說法。"},{"pid":"8e55ef1f991c3784905338cc9068e87b1128600d","tid":590953,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"高通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342c06bc9c9e19dd92a0f29cdbcb0a78ed13b150","tid":590953,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"高通真係仆街黎"},{"pid":"0b09ea3cb458128ea5f3992390191aca5d8bfce6","tid":590953,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":47,"score":-47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"高呼民主背後還是獨裁，美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2078307cd09d21a97e92b53f4d940cb69339e0","tid":590953,"uid":118988,"like":1,"dislike":41,"score":-40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"高呼民主背後還是獨裁，美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05aa65942a1f3235f3e0298a91585c27cfcfa81","tid":590953,"uid":66943,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"0b09ea3cb458128ea5f3992390191aca5d8bfce6","tid":590953,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":47,"score":-47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"高呼民主背後還是獨裁，美國<img src=\"